# 🧠 OS Concept 2: Consistency vs Availability

🔥 Very famous tradeoff question.

---

# 🔹 Consistency

All users see same latest data.

---

# 🔹 Availability

System always responds.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Bank balance 💳

Consistency:

Everyone sees exact latest amount.

Availability:

ATM always works even during updates.

---

## ⚙️ Important Insight

In distributed systems:

Sometimes improving one reduces the other.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Difference between consistency and availability?**

👉 Consistency ensures same data, availability ensures system responsiveness.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="4n2x8s"
Consistency = same data
Availability = always responds
```

